1957;;Kill Me Tomorrow;;British;;Terence Fisher;;Pat O'Brien, Lois Maxwell;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kill_Me_Tomorrow;;After suffering a series of personal setbacks and in desperate need of cash, reporter Bart Crosbie tries to get his old job back. But when he returns to the newspaper offices, Crosbie discovers that his former boss has been murdered. He is then offered money by the killer, a diamond smuggler, to take the murder rap.